As of this moment my journal was switched into "friends-only" mode. I will not give the reasons here because I am not even sure about that myself.

If you do not have a livejournal account and I cannot add you as my friend, there is another option: use <lj user="friendofdumike">'s journal. Just go to that journal and follow the instructions. If that does not work for you, it simply means that you have no business to read my journal.

Mike.
